        <item>
            <title>【实试】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳机　主动降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒适</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dyson-ontrac</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:01:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson OnTrac]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[无线蓝牙耳机]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1250555</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Dyson 今日宣布推出首款高保真、纯音频的降噪耳机 Dyson OnTrac。这款耳机具有先进的降噪功能，更备有长达 55 小时特强续航力，充电一次可使用 2 星期。今日 Dyson 就邀请了小娴和小编亲身体验 Dyson OnTrac。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-26-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>宽广音频范围</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 配备 40 mm、16 ohm 的钕合金喇叭驱动器，可重现低至 6Hz 和高达 21,000 Hz 的频率，呈现深沉低音和清晰高音的细腻音色。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250895" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲钕合金喇叭驱动器</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/4-9-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲扬声器外壳配合耳朵倾斜 13 度，营造更直接的音效体验。</p><h2>8 个主动降噪麦克风　可消除 40 dB 噪音</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 采用个人化主动降噪演算法，使用 8 个主动降噪麦克风，每秒对外部声音进行达 384,000 次取样。配合优质材料和精心设计的内部几何结构，耳机可消除 40 dB 噪音。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250894" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/dyson-supersonic-nural/pretty01/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic Nural 新一代智能风筒香港发布  3 大智能感测科技、按距离调温保护头皮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>可个人化变换耳机外壳及耳垫</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 有四种配色，现提供亮银色、亮铜色和黑钢色等配色选项。陶瓷朱砂色则采用了陶瓷质感的喷漆表面处理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250821" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-630x580.jpg" alt="" width="630" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-630x580.jpg 630w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-2-scaled.jpg 978w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 630px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲多种颜色和饰面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250834" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10-694x389.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10-694x389.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dysonontracheadphone-10.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250901" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6-473x580.jpg" alt="" width="473" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6-473x580.jpg 473w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/12-6.jpg 734w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 473px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/14-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/16-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2></h2><h2>佩戴感：不觉夹耳　三点式分布平衡重量</h2><p>小编初初看见 Dyson OnTrac 时觉得耳机看起来很大，以为肯定会很笨重，但实际佩戴时居然意想不到的轻盈。试戴最先感受到的是其平衡的重量分布设计。一般头戴式耳机重量不是集中在头顶，就是会过份「夹耳」，但 Dyson OnTrac 采用三点式分布设计，重量平均分布在双耳和头顶，佩戴时不会觉得有任何位置特别受力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-11-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>耳垫的材质让小编印象深刻。耳垫海绵非常软熟，官方称其为「微绒面」，实际触感类似滑身麖皮，非常亲肤，材质摸起来似乎应该不会起毛粒。耳垫采用「高密度泡棉」，柔软之余回弹力强，大力按压后亦可迅速回复原状（见下面影片），提供极舒适的佩戴感，长时间佩戴应该不会觉得耳朵疼痛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250871" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/18-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="padding: 100% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="dyson_OnTrac_耳垫" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/985431167?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「高密度泡棉」耳垫</p><p>刚刚戴上头时会感觉到头带有些微压力，但在调校好头带长度后，配合特厚海绵「卸力」，小编没有特别觉得不舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6-6-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="text-align: center;">▲可调式头带 + 特厚海绵</div><div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1250873" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><div style="text-align: center;">▲头带采用多轴万向式支架设计确保重量平均分布</div><div></div><div style="padding: 100% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="dyson_OnTrac_test 头带" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/985431117?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲头带的海绵非常软熟</p><p>音色方面，小编今次仅是走马看花，蜻蜓点水式试听过一阵，无法给予太多意见，但粗略来说 Dyson OnTrac 人声表现清晰，音色细腻，高频部分尤为突出。</p><h2>其他功能</h2><ul><li>头部感应：当用家取下耳机时，电容式感测器会自动侦测，并发出暂停音讯的信号。重新戴上耳机后，则自动恢复音讯。</li><li>直观的操控杆：可轻松播放、暂停、跳过、快进和倒退曲目，或按住进行语音指令。</li><li>清晰的通话：双波束形成的麦克风能清晰地接收你的声音，而非外界噪音。</li><li>实时声音追踪：持续监测耳内和外界音量，并通过应用程式中的即时报告显示可能有害的高音量。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1250966 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-17-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/18/dyson-supersonic-nural/pretty01/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Dyson Supersonic Nural 新一代智能风筒香港发布  3 大智能感测科技、按距离调温保护头皮</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/">【实试】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳机　主动降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒适</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
